title: Genesis Live Shepperton 1973
description:
Genesis live in Shepperton 1973:

Watcher Of The Skies
Dancing With The Moonlit Knight
I Know What I Like (In Your Wardrobe)
The Musical Box
Supper's Ready

Lineup:
Peter Gabriel - lead vocals, flute, percussion
Steve Hackett - lead electric and acoustic guitars
Michael Rutherford - bass, guitars, bass pedals, vocals
Tony Banks - keyboards, acoustic 12-string guitar, vocals
Phil Collins - drums and percussion, vocals

Enjoy!
